<BlogPost
  title="How to Stop Doomscrolling: 8 Methods That Actually Work"
  description="The standard advice — put your phone in another room — treats the symptom, not the system. Here's what's actually happening when you doomscroll, and eight approaches that address it at the right level."
  publishDate="2026-03-17"
